    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a 2004 Porsche 911 Turbo, a pinnacle of German engineering featuring the 3.6L Mezger flat-six with integrated dry-sump lubrication. This twin-turbocharged unit sends power through a reinforced 6-speed manual transaxle to a sophisticated AWD system. The vehicle features four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers and an active aero rear wing. Recent service includes a full cooling system refresh and coil pack replacement. Though it displays light aesthetic wear, its mechanical synchronization and boost delivery are impeccable, making it a perfect candidate for the discerning driver who prioritizes performance over concours perfection.",
