    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that strikes a perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the leather upholstery is clean and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All interior electronics, from the premium audio system to the heated seats and navigation, are in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule, recently completing a full fluid service and a brake inspection. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need a replacement anytime soon. Included with the sale are two sets of keys and a comprehensive file of service receipts. This is a solid, honest car ready for its next owner.",
